data.description: You've arrived at a distinctive and timeless Villa behind the gates of Signature at PGA West, the perfect desert hideaway.  This floor plan features contemporary finishes with four en-suite bedrooms, three walk-in closets, a powder room, two private patios and a balcony.  The gourmet kitchen has a large island, generous cabinet space, and is open to an intimate dining area and patio.  Centrally located at PGA West where you can take in the panoramic natural beauty of the Santa Rosa Mountains, a majestic setting for indoor-outdoor activities and desert adventures.  Offered furnished, this short-term rental friendly property also makes a great investment opportunity with many attractive accommodations for future guests.  Relax and unwind at the Signature Clubhouse.  Cool off in the resort-style pool, enjoy the outdoor barbecue area, and private gym.
